Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.47,0:00:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很少人知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.78,0:00:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.51,0:00:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，就說別這樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再逗我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.49,0:00:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是急性子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正夜晚還長得很
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢來…好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這片朗朗晴空裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:01:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的心情 飛散灑滿其中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.03,0:01:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果命中註定的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.10,0:01:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠是你那該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現實卻無法如願以償
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在閃耀光芒的風裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想的羽毛 飄然落下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣邁向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就這麼美麗地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始奔騰的熱烈心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.57,0:01:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躍動出跟那一天同樣的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你率直的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.81,0:02:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能永遠看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第6話 燃燒17歲（^^;）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也已經國二了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也該稍微長大一點了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別老是像個小孩子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.41,0:02:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有長大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.81,0:02:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說這個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，對了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，這次的打工你沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟陣爺爺都來拜託我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來還要找一個男生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和兩個女生啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你有沒有認識適合人選？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被妳這麼一問我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碧要辭職了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到其他正職工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說正職…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳幾歲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17歲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17歲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說是17歲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近有點脫離本行的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就趁這個機會下定決心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人一旦決定要做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得要認真做!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碧妳真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說是絲毫不迷惘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請教我人生的道理啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜最近也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜妳等等啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在她在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫忙結婚典禮？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟巧海…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有命也一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙的爺爺家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在這附近的神社
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是很有歷史的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做"封架神社"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前說到\N很便宜的收驚就是這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不用多問
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也該好好說明一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常我們家是不主持婚禮的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就是有人不斷拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才需要找人幫忙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳啊，生什麼氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要 都給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是好人!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，這樣至少湊齊人數了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好啦，反正我週末沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海也想打工看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說反而剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是啊，詩帆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想問啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份打工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需不需要多一個\N非～常能幹的幫手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳剛剛不是說反正都最後了\N所以才調班到週末的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還挺硬性調班的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小碧翹班的話\N會只剩下小茜一個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣好壞心～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太久沒爬…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真累人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海，行李讓我拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點東西，沒問題的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦，大家加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，不好意思喔\N讓你們特地跑來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家老太婆過世之後\N就從沒主持過婚禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真是幫了大忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先請你們幫忙從這裡搬出\N婚禮上需要用到的道具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.42,0:07:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要點菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的餐還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我加水好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結帳喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的餐還沒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬…馬上來…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳上哪去了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點喔，那邊有高低差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間也要整理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是不可以打開的門
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是神社\N流傳下來的故事就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說裡面關著很久以前\N在城鎮上大肆胡鬧的可怕惡神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果打開的話就會引發災難
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近\N對這種事情也不能一笑置之
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之不去招惹惡神\N就不會引發災禍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是這些了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的只能一點一點搬了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然體積大，但是並不會很重\N肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許可以一次搬完
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有東西忘了拿吧？走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罷，有狀況就拿出壓箱寶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.51,0:09:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥居是清的"江戶紫"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本是宇田川的"濱千鳥"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.62,0:09:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不只春畫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽玄的"和漢千祭圖錄"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東賴坊的"伊予封略演義"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是寶山啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,供應食宿還可以泡澡\N又有錢拿的打工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一生下來就有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡的時候可以看得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個也？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看…看起來很像對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得很意外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆的皮膚真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲毫沒有皺紋耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要摸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，詩帆妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮在洗澡水上面耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～討厭，妳好賊喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.98,0:10:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罵我賊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦\N她們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不是知道我們在這裡\N還故意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照這樣子看來\N你跟詩帆應該沒有什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪可能有啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒出息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你分明就\N看過詩帆的裸體很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是幼稚園的時候耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實想把那個大奶妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.97,0:10:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話了，你這臭老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.18,0:10:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好像來畢業旅行一樣\N很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是還好啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尿尿…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廁所在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的新娘的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奶奶的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺說將來等我嫁人的時候\N要給我穿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我的哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳!不要把我的哥哥搶走!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不可能的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:11:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥一定喜歡大胸部嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣學姐的胸部又大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且最近妳們之間\N好像又有所交集
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的很喜歡那傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他之間\N沒有妳所擔心的那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳可以幫我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我跟哥哥\N可以湊成恩愛的一對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆妳也是很直呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.44,0:12:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK，我就幫妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也不知道\N我能幫什麼就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣學姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡妳了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩…詩帆？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等!命!住手啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，她們真的很吵耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很癢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一學長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…你真的對姊姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把那個老頭講的話當真啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種難搞又好強的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可敬謝不敏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過她也有溫柔的一面喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是戀姊癖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早點睡吧，明天還要早起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要聲明不是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.91,0:13:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新娘們到了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那麼，出動啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差別真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過份!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼今天一整天就拜託你們啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然封印還沒破除
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:14:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我想也是時間問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為\N這是葬送那個的大好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也不打算插手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白小姐，很適合妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，二三
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是舞衣同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是適合婚禮的好天氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位也都受到邀請了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是學生會的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單來說\N新娘的父親是本校理事之一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後新郎是我的學弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來，舞衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件衣服還真適合妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦，神崎學長真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不，我是說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我心動了一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，真是太榮幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣學姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，你們請自便
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為不應該\N調戲那種沒經驗的女生唷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留同學\N妳這麼說真讓我意外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼連陽子老師都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你扮豬吃老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經早上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋笨蛋，我是大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這滿溢的知性\N和好奇心實在可恨，太可恨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.53,0:15:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，反省完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上陣啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就確認過這麼多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣，我很期待妳唷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對是這扇門沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來\N我的論文就可以完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞…舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊…\N要含著淚聽，含著淚講
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有著比\N馬里亞納海溝更深～的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能撕掉啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.18,0:16:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快!快貼回去啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何？為什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會引發災害的!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破封印
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是舞衣公主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是什麼地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HiME？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碧!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來\N就得跟那幅畫說再見了哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碧!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.99,0:17:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖我同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:17:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來遲了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫妳的心之子出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想連累外面的客人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個迦具土\N擅自亂衝亂撞的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳收服無法控制的玩意\N又是要幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.09,0:18:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無依者…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自古以來\N就是威脅人類的妖魔鬼怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類在恐懼之中\N渡過了痛苦的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，心中抱著熱忱鬥魂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一名果敢挺身\N面對怪物的少女出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她名叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈風的HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉浦碧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們還太嫩了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從無依者的魔掌之中解救人類\N是我們HiME的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對抗邪惡無須迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更別說同伴之間起內訌了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守護世界的口令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義與愛和友情!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友情？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來吧!鋼之牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愕 ．天． 王～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愕天王？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做就要認真做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愕天王～!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍捲～風
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地因車輪的聲響而怒吼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愕天王!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋～～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怒衝破一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶喊!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必勝!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾敬畏地道出伊邪那歧大神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.21,0:21:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與筑紫的日向…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碧，謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別謝別謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來，弄破封印的是我\N我錯在先
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幅壁畫…是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還要再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我的論文完成了\N我會第一個讓妳看的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.00,0:21:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,論文？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.46,0:21:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果小碧妳到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個沒辦法拿來當飯吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.01,0:21:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:22:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我代替住院的澤田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.51,0:22:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責教導本班日本史
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.85,0:22:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫杉浦碧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就叫我小碧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「請別迷惘」\N這句話我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有無法傳達給你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.80,0:22:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過寂寞的笑容搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.14,0:22:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫過傷口 Lonely good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.38,0:22:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連熱情都會讓我痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追尋著永恆的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.86,0:22:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾是我的天空我的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.73,0:22:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那段燃燒熔化的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.24,0:23:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘記 要時時想起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只是收藏在心底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Search for my life\N總有一天還會再相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.79,0:23:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是喜歡你那清澈的雙眼\N現在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走上各自的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.10,0:23:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新開始前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.55,0:23:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷途的小貓們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷途的小貓們\N小碧啊，妳到底是幾歲呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.05,0:23:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說我17歲了啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.92,0:23:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是既然妳能當老師…\N鴇羽同學
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.12,0:23:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.22,0:23:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師如果說她是17歲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.89,0:23:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是17歲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.39,0:23:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以過份追究
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.00,0:24:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開始搬到爺爺的神社\N所在的風華町
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.53,0:24:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在我剛滿五歲的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.47,0:24:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實說老實話，我非常排斥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.91,0:24:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大家分離\N來到這個小小的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.74,0:24:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我很常哭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.48,0:24:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人孤單地哭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.41,0:24:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直到那個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.68,0:24:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我遇到哥哥為止
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.99,0:24:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他並不是白馬王子那種型
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.12,0:24:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在我眼中\N他卻是白馬王子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.12,0:24:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他並不是英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.89,0:24:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，對我而言他卻是英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.90,0:24:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛惡作劇，又壞心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.50,0:24:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻非常體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.23,0:24:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是詩帆的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.40,0:24:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.90,0:24:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.27,0:24:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想叫他"祐一哥哥"看看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.14,0:24:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，如果我這樣叫的話\N我們之間的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.68,0:24:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會有所改變
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.05,0:24:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還是維持這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.99,0:24:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當哥哥的妹妹就好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.19,0:25:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.46,0:25:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.99,0:25:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.36,0:25:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆最喜歡哥哥了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.30,0:23:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,


